    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, serving as a reliable and comfortable choice for any driver. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts exactly as it should, providing a confident driving experience. The interior is clean and shows only minor signs of regular use, while the exterior remains well-preserved with a healthy finish. It has been a dependable vehicle, and its next owner can expect continued performance and comfort for many miles to come.",
      "price": 35000.0,
